Flip at 4: [1, 7, 3, 6, 10]
Flip at 2: [7, 1, 3, 6, 10]
Flip at 3: [3, 1, 7, 6, 10]
Flip at 2: [1, 3, 7, 6, 10]
Flip at 3: [7, 3, 1, 6, 10]
