        // Set values using setters
        s.setName("Hari");
        s.setMarks(88);

        // Get values using getters
        System.out.println("Name: " + s.getName());
        System.out.println("Marks: " + s.getMarks());
    }
}
ğŸ”’ Why you canâ€™t do this directly:
java
Copy
